<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/_header') %>
    <title>Billsplit - Example</title>
    <!-- LINKS TO EXTERNAL STYLESHEETS
            format: rel="/stylesheets/example.css" -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/howTo.css">
    <style>
        /* page specific style declarations */
    </style>
    
</head>
    
<body>
    <div id="pageContainer">
        <!-- HEADER STUFF, CAN IGNORE -->
        <%- include('../partials/_nav') %>

        <!-- ALL PAGE CONTENT INSIDE HERE -->
        <div class="container" style ="margin-top: 2.5rem; display:flex">
            <div class="questions">
                <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">How do I start splitting a bill?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>From the homepage, you can either click "Get Started" or "Split a Receipt"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">How do I add people?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>In the calculator, type in someone's name and hit 'enter' key to add another person. Once you have everyone, click 'Finish' </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">What if I made a mistake inputting names/items?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>If you make a mistake, double click on anything to make edit it, you can also use the back button to visit a previous section</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">What if not everyone is sharing an item?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>After inputting an item, simply type in the initials of each person whom it's shared by, alternatively you can type 'all - jb' to exclude j, b. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">What if an item isn't shared equally?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>To split an item unevenly, just type the same initial multiple times. For example, if John is using 2/3 of the eggs and Mary is using 1/3 of the eggs, you can type "jjm".</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">Do I have to type everyone's initial to add everyone to an item?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>Nope. You can simply type "all" for everybody when prompted for initials. Alternatively, you could type "all-jm" to exclude John and Mary</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                    <button class="accordion">Can I add a tip?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>To add a tip, increase the tax percentage to account for tip as well.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                    <button class="accordion">Can I send the receipt to someone else in my group?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>Yes. First, log in or create an account. Then process your receipt. Hit save at the end and then use the share button to add the username of your friends.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                    <button class="accordion">I'm still confused, how does it work?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>If you closely read and follow the instructions on the receipt splitter, it will guide you through the process.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h1>Account Questions</h1>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">I forgot my password?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>We only store encrypted passwords, so if you <a href="/contact">contact us</a> we can email you a new password.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">Is my information secure?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>All passwords are stored with industry-standard encryption, personal data is also encrypted and cannot be stolen by hackers. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bcrypt"> Learn More</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="question">
                    <button class="accordion">Are you tracking my data?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                    <p>We believe in data tracking transparency. We do not currently sell any user data, although we do keep records of users receipts. 
                        <br><br>    If you wish to not have your data stored, <a href="/logOut">log out</a> and don't use your account. If 
                        you would like to request for us to delete your data, contact us <a href="/contact">here.</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>  
        </div>       
        
        <!-- FOOTER CAN IGNORE -->
        <%- include('../partials/_footer') %>
    </div>
    
</body> 
    <!-- get username information, sorry it's named guestUser
            gives access to set and delete username functions -->
    <%- include('../partials/_guestUser') %>

    <!-- LINKS TO EXTERNAL FUNCTION SCRIPTS
         format: src"/scripts/example.js" --> 
    
    <!-- Page Executable -->
    <script>
        var acc = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");
        var i;
        
        for (i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {
          acc[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
            this.classList.toggle("active");
            var panel = this.nextElementSibling;
            if (panel.style.maxHeight) {
              panel.style.maxHeight = null;
            } else {
              panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + "px";
            } 
          });
        }
    </script>
       
    

</html>